Class Asterisk

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kordamp.jsilhouette.javafx.AbstractSilhouette
      • org.kordamp.jsilhouette.javafx.AbstractCenteredSilhouette
        • org.kordamp.jsilhouette.javafx.Asterisk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CenteredSilhouette, Silhouette
    public class Asterisk
extends AbstractCenteredSilhouette
    Asterisk

    Defines an asterisk shape that may have round corners.

    Constraints

    • beamCount > 1
    • 0 <= roundness <= 1
    • width <= radius* 2

    Style Classes

    • silhouette
    • silhouette-asterisk
    Author:
    Andres Almiray
